# Technical Architecture

## System Stack & Topology

## Frontend Stack

- **Framework**: React 18 (Vite-powered SPA)
- **Visuals**: ReactFlow v11 for interactive graph rendering
- **Styling**: Vanilla CSS for high-fidelity custom glassmorphic styling
- **Networking**: Axios with interceptors for JWT token rotation and authentication lifecycle

## Backend Stack

- **Web Framework**: FastAPI (Python 3.11+)
- **WSGI/ASGI**: Uvicorn server
- **Database Driver**: Motor (asyncio MongoDB driver)
- **Cryptography**: cryptography.fernet for encrypting GitHub PATs at rest
- **LLM Integrations**: Claude Sonnet 4.5 via the Emergent integrations platform, with fallback to local Llama 3 models

## Execution Topology

Client Browser (Zustand + ReactFlow) ──[JSON API via JWT]──> FastAPI App ──[Async Driver]──> MongoDB Instance

