## FastAPI Route Definitions

## REST API Architecture

### Authentication

- `POST /api/auth/register` -> TokenResponse
- `POST /api/auth/login` -> TokenResponse
- `POST /api/auth/refresh` -> TokenResponse (rotating JWT flow)
- `POST /api/auth/logout` -> SuccessResponse (revoking refresh JTI)

### Project Management

- `GET /api/projects` -> List[Project]
- `POST /api/projects` -> Project
- `GET /api/projects/{id}` -> Project
- `PUT /api/projects/{id}` -> Project
- `DELETE /api/projects/{id}` -> SuccessResponse

### Canvas Data

- `GET /api/projects/{id}/nodes` -> List[Node]
- `POST /api/projects/{id}/nodes` -> Node
- `PUT /api/nodes/{id}` -> Node
- `DELETE /api/nodes/{id}` -> SuccessResponse
- `GET /api/projects/{id}/edges` -> List[Edge]
- `POST /api/projects/{id}/edges` -> Edge
- `DELETE /api/edges/{id}` -> SuccessResponse

### AI & Integrations

- `POST /api/projects/{id}/repository` -> ConnectRepoResponse
